Question: Both images are top views showing at least six cymbals per image along with multiple cylindrical drums.

Reference Answer: True

Left image URL: https://i.pinimg.com/736x/db/06/7b/db067b3bf79988a24bc3862ca32b9e01--double-bass-drums.jpg

Right image URL: https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/originals/ae/10/f2/ae10f2189197b07633a46c61642e1ebc.jpg

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is the image a top view?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is the image a top view?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many cymbals are in the image?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many cymbals are in the image?')
ANSWER4=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Are there multiple cylindrical drums in the image?')
ANSWER5=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Are there multiple cylindrical drums in the image?')
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} and {ANSWER1} and {ANSWER2} >= 6 and {ANSWER4} and {ANSWER5}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER6)
```
